Steps for Installation
--------------------------
Manual Installation
PHP
Mysql
Netdata
S3cmd - for backup only

HOSTED
1. set .my.cnf with correct user name and password
2. set config.sh file env settings

DEDICATED SERVER
1. copy deployment script of latest version / particular version.
2. set config.sh file env settings

Steps for Updating
--------------------------
FIRST TIME UPDATING
1. stop cron job - comment out cron job entry.
2. Rename existing folders for web , service and api.
3. update config.sh file for current env
4. Rename Existing DB with Licence "CompanyNameRM" , "CompanyNameBilling" , "CompanyNameCDR" , "CompanyNameReport" etc.



check in config.sh file for db names.
